g.text: UML Diagram: Class RevisableDatum in Context
- Move the mouse cursor over a name to see more information.
- Click on a name to go to the corresponding page.
- The arrows of the inheritance tree are

a.title: ― Revision: Algorithm applied to produce a revised datum.
a.xlink:title: ― Revision: Algorithm applied to produce a revised datum.

a.title: ― ScopedMeasure: A qualified measure whose domain is a universe as an aggregate, i.e. a measure with a specific production method applied to a specific cell in a cube.
a.xlink:title: ― ScopedMeasure: A qualified measure whose domain is a universe as an aggregate, i.e. a measure with a specific production method applied to a specific cell in a cube.

a.title: ― InstanceValue: Single data instance corresponding to a concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceValue: Single data instance corresponding to a concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived.

a.title: ― InstanceVariable: Use of a represented variable within a data set.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceVariable: Use of a represented variable within a data set.

a.title: ― ConceptualValue: Concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived which is associated to a single data instance.
a.xlink:title: ― ConceptualValue: Concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived which is associated to a single data instance.

a.title: ― Datum: Correspondence of a data instance to the concept it represents.
a.xlink:title: ― Datum: Correspondence of a data instance to the concept it represents.

a.title: ― CatalogDetails: A set of information useful for attribution, data discovery, and access.
a.xlink:title: ― CatalogDetails: A set of information useful for attribution, data discovery, and access.

a.title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.
a.xlink:title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.

a.title: ― generates: Scoped measure generates one revisable datum.
a.xlink:title: ― generates: Scoped measure generates one revisable datum.

a.title: ― isBoundedBy: A datum is bounded by an instance variable. The datum is drawn from a set of values, either substantive or sentinel described by the value domain of the instance variable.
a.xlink:title: ― isBoundedBy: A datum is bounded by an instance variable. The datum is drawn from a set of values, either substantive or sentinel described by the value domain of the instance variable.
